巴打如果識煮飯不妨去當地開餐廳應該賺到fatfat , 因為個邊啲人廚藝好水皮</blockquote><br />\n又最美的風景是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個到遠離支那、日本、歐美，應該做遠洋漁業好搶手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打想去個到應該唔怕凍、悶，克服埋大浪應該可以試下漁業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps，個度d海流支那人幫佢起左個朵，叫魔鬼西風帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日都狂風大浪，風速講緊平均7-8級（對應返香港，即係每日都吹緊強風-烈風，即係每日都掛緊3-8號波）如果撞正風暴就吹𩗗風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，每個月都平均有2-5個風暴形成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時返到香港就可以笑鳩香港人未見過風浪<br />\n<br />\n係澳洲做過南極觀鯨船攝影師助手2個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，跟左一次之後唔會再想去個條西風帶，痴撚線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a880e8c82d98f28391bb57dfa850af6cd87375b","tid":386403,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>明年小弟畢業馬上打算過去闖蕩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然咩資料都未搵，打算問問巴絲建議/詳情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就一齊交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凍到仆街<br />\n亞南極氣候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該慘過冰島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打下年畢業的話，撞正南半球冬天<br />\n巴打買定ps4過去打，日照時間應該好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji